        <abstract> 
<p>Has prepared a historical sketch [of writers on origin of species] for foreign editions of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. It includes HS. He was too ill to provide it for the 1st ed.</p>  
<p>Sorry Murray has not sent HS his copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, as he was instructed.</p> 
            <p>Huxley will put CD and E. A. Darwin down for HS’s gigantic [publishing] programme. Suggests Dr Drysdale be approached about it.</p>
        </abstract>
